---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ExampleCard from '../components/ExampleCard.astro';
---

<Layout title="ChatAndBuild Examples">
	<div class="container">
		<h1>Example Projects with <span class="text-gradient">ChatAndBuild</span></h1>
		<p class="intro">Browse these example projects to get inspiration for your own creations. Each example includes a description of what was built and how it was accomplished using ChatAndBuild.</p>
		
		<div class="filters">
			<button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
			<button class="filter-btn" data-filter="Beginner">Beginner</button>
			<button class="filter-btn" data-filter="Intermediate">Intermediate</button>
			<button class="filter-btn" data-filter="Advanced">Advanced</button>
		</div>
		
		<div class="examples-grid">
			<ExampleCard 
				title="Personal Portfolio" 
				description="A clean, responsive portfolio website with sections for about, skills, projects, and contact information."
				image="/images/example-portfolio.png"
				link="/examples/portfolio"
				difficulty="Beginner"
			/>
			
			<ExampleCard 
				title="Recipe Finder App" 
				description="Search for recipes by ingredients, save favorites, and get step-by-step cooking instructions."
				image="/images/example-recipe.png"
				link="/examples/recipe-finder"
				difficulty="Beginner"
			/>
			
			<ExampleCard 
				title="Task Management Dashboard" 
				description="A Trello-like task management app with drag-and-drop functionality and user authentication."
				image="/images/example-tasks.png"
				link="/examples/task-manager"
				difficulty="Intermediate"
			/>
			
			<ExampleCard 
				title="E-commerce Store" 
				description="A complete online store with product listings, shopping cart, and checkout process."
				image="/images/example-ecommerce.png"
				link="/examples/ecommerce"
				difficulty="Intermediate"
			/>
			
			<ExampleCard 
				title="Social Media Dashboard" 
				description="Track and analyze your social media presence across multiple platforms in one dashboard."
				image="/images/example-social.png"
				link="/examples/social-dashboard"
				difficulty="Intermediate"
			/>
			
			<ExampleCard 
				title="Real-time Chat Application" 
				description="A Slack-like chat application with real-time messaging, channels, and direct messages."
				image="/images/example-chat.png"
				link="/examples/chat-app"
				difficulty="Advanced"
			/>
		</div>
		
		<h2>How to Use These Examples</h2>
		<p>These examples are meant to inspire your own projects and show what's possible with ChatAndBuild. Here's how to make the most of them:</p>
		
		<div class="step-container">
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">1</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Explore the Examples</h3>
					<p>Click on any example to see more details about how it was built, including the initial prompt used, key features, and screenshots of the final product.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">2</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Use as a Starting Point</h3>
					<p>When starting a new project in ChatAndBuild, you can reference these examples in your initial prompt. For instance: "I'd like to build something similar to the Recipe Finder example, but focused on cocktail recipes instead."</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="step">
				<div class="step-number">3</div>
				<div class="step-content">
					<h3>Mix and Match Features</h3>
					<p>You don't have to copy an example exactly. Feel free to combine features from different examples or add your own unique ideas.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="tip">
			<strong>Tip:</strong> When describing your project to ChatAndBuild, it's helpful to mention specific features or design elements you like from these examples. This gives the AI a clearer understanding of your vision.
		</div>
		
		<h2>Start with a Template</h2>
		<p>If you're not sure where to begin, you can ask ChatAndBuild to start with one of these templates. Just mention the example name in your initial prompt:</p>
		
		<div class="example-prompt">
			<p>"I'd like to start with the Personal Portfolio template and customize it for my photography business."</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="cta-box">
			<h3>Have an Idea? Build It Now!</h3>
			<p>Ready to create your own project inspired by these examples? Start a new conversation with ChatAndBuild and bring your idea to life!</p>
			<a href="https://www.chatandbuild.com" target="_blank" class="btn">Create New Project</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<script>
	// Filter functionality for examples
	document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
		const filterButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn');
		const examples = document.querySelectorAll('.example-card');
		
		filterButtons.forEach(button => {
			button.addEventListener('click', () => {
				// Update active button
				filterButtons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
				button.classList.add('active');
				
				// Filter examples
				const filter = button.getAttribute('data-filter');
				
				examples.forEach(example => {
					if (filter === 'all') {
						example.style.display = 'block';
					} else {
						const difficulty = example.querySelector('.difficulty-badge').textContent.trim();
						example.style.display = difficulty === filter ? 'block' : 'none';
					}
				});
			});
		});
	});
</script>

<style>
	.intro {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.filters {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	
	.filter-btn {
		background: none;
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--primary));
		color: rgb(var(--primary));
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 9999px;
		cursor: pointer;
		font-weight: 500;
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}
	
	.filter-btn:hover {
		background-color: rgba(var(--primary), 0.1);
	}
	
	.filter-btn.active {
		background-color: rgb(var(--primary));
		color: white;
	}
	
	.examples-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}
	
	.example-prompt {
		background-color: rgba(var(--primary), 0.1);
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1rem;
		margin: 1rem 0;
		border-left: 4px solid rgb(var(--primary));
	}
	
	.example-prompt p {
		margin: 0;
		font-style: italic;
	}
	
	.cta-box {
		background-color: rgba(var(--primary), 0.1);
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 2rem;
		margin-top: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	
	.cta-box h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
	}
	
	.cta-box .btn {
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.examples-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
